headline: Northern Trust Accelerates New Business Momentum with Institutional Asset Owners in 2025
summary: CHICAGO, LONDON & MELBOURNE, December 09, 2025--Northern Trust announced more than 100 asset servicing mandates across key global markets in 2025, representing more than US$385 billion in assets.
